#. <section class="sutta" id="sn11.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn11.21:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 11"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga"
msgstr "3. The Third Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 21. Chetvāsutta → jhatvāsuttaṃ (bj, pts2) | ghatvāsuttaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn11.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Chetvāsutta"
msgstr "21. Incinerated"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.237"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn11.21:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane."
msgstr "Near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove."

msgctxt "sn11.21:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sakko devānamindo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"And then Sakka, lord of gods, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one "
"side,"

msgctxt "sn11.21:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho sakko devānamindo bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.509"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn11.21:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsu chetvā sukhaṃ seti,"
msgstr "“When what is incinerated do you sleep at ease?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:2.2"
msgid "kiṃsu chetvā na socati;"
msgstr "When what is incinerated is there no sorrow?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:2.3"
msgid "Kissassu ekadhammassa,"
msgstr "What is the one thing"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:2.4"
msgid "vadhaṃ rocesi gotamā”ti."
msgstr "whose killing you approve?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn11.21:3.1"
msgid "“Kodhaṃ chetvā sukhaṃ seti,"
msgstr "“When anger’s incinerated you sleep at ease."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:3.2"
msgid "kodhaṃ chetvā na socati;"
msgstr "When anger’s incinerated there is no sorrow."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:3.3"
msgid "Kodhassa visamūlassa,"
msgstr "O Vāsava, anger has a poisoned root"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:3.4"
msgid "madhuraggassa vāsava;"
msgstr "and a honey tip."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:3.5"
msgid "Vadhaṃ ariyā pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "The noble ones praise its killing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn11.21:3.6"
msgid "tañhi chetvā na socatī”ti."
msgstr "for when it’s incinerated there is no sorrow.”"
